      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "## Demoboard Discovery\nUtiliser ce dashboard pour un premier tour des signaux avant d'aller dans les UIs dédiées.\n\n- **Metrics** : Golden signals et santé infra\n- **Logs** : OpenSearch datasource pour les logs JSON corrélés\n- **Traces** : Jaeger pour suivre `trace_id` entre API et worker\n\nLes `trace_id` sont présents dans les logs applicatifs de `api-service` et `worker-service`.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.5.2",
      "title": "Guide",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "reqps"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(rate(demoboard_api_requests_total[5m]))",
